  "detailed_description": "<strong>Bring Your Imagination To Life!</strong><br><br>In the Magnetic Structures game , you can make different magnet 3D structures and enjoy connecting the colourful rods to the metal balls. Each level is designed for you to make a specific structure by following the provided pattern. Pay attention to the details such as colours and location of the parts to make your structure identical to the provided example.<br><br>Let the magnet do its work. Use simple tools to build complicated structures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/057c42a7d49c451ceb3a372e4587bbd1.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/b16af2e4d45124a77f83d10b989bd272.poster.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/b16af2e4d45124a77f83d10b989bd272.webm?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/b16af2e4d45124a77f83d10b989bd272.mp4?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bring the spheres and magnet bars together to connect them. As simple as that, this is the basis of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/710f7aaa0393526f57835c1c985515cf.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/cb6ca0f89071099b061fad223fc90ff9.poster.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/cb6ca0f89071099b061fad223fc90ff9.webm?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/cb6ca0f89071099b061fad223fc90ff9.mp4?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From the bottom of the screen you can activate different options such turning off the gravity; This options can assist you with building larger and more complicated structures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/6f90f643d03cf7d25b271ba10aa9d264.poster.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/6f90f643d03cf7d25b271ba10aa9d264.webm?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/6f90f643d03cf7d25b271ba10aa9d264.mp4?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/44db075c05238d824ecee11d0176b146.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>In order to successfully pass each level, you have to complete the requested structure according to the map. Place each part in its place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/09d1ae5d15bf15b499d793ede0a2b129.poster.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/09d1ae5d15bf15b499d793ede0a2b129.webm?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/09d1ae5d15bf15b499d793ede0a2b129.mp4?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Please note the game is currently in early access, any comment or recommendation would be appreciated so we can consider them upon the full release of the game. Our goal is to make the game-play as enjoyable as possible for the players so leave your recommendation in community-hub , leave a review or directly email them to us.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Bring Your Imagination To Life!</strong><br><br>In the Magnetic Structures game , you can make different magnet 3D structures and enjoy connecting the colourful rods to the metal balls. Each level is designed for you to make a specific structure by following the provided pattern. Pay attention to the details such as colours and location of the parts to make your structure identical to the provided example.<br><br>Let the magnet do its work. Use simple tools to build complicated structures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/057c42a7d49c451ceb3a372e4587bbd1.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/b16af2e4d45124a77f83d10b989bd272.poster.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/b16af2e4d45124a77f83d10b989bd272.webm?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/b16af2e4d45124a77f83d10b989bd272.mp4?t=1731486935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Bring the spheres and magnet bars together to connect them. As simple as that, this is the basis of the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/710f7aaa0393526f57835c1c985515cf.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1923900/extras/cb6ca0f89071099b061fad223fc90ff9.poster.avif?t=1731486935\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://share